This paper deals with event detection, which is a sub-task of natural language processing (NLP). Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CL (Computation and Language). The paper also proposes a novel approach that involves meta-learning and dynamic memory networks, which are techniques commonly used in machine learning and artificial intelligence. Therefore, cs.LG (Machine Learning), cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence), and cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing) are also likely categories. Finally, the paper involves processing textual data, which is often done using techniques from computer vision, such as convolutional neural networks. Therefore, cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition) is also a possible category.
